data.description:
This must see three bedroom two bathroom home with office or 4th bedroom is situated in the Home Place subdivision, known for its convenient proximity to IH-35 and shopping. This location can be advantageous for commuting or accessing nearby amenities.
The 3 car garage features tandem parking, allowing room for an ATV, golf cart, or even a workshop area.
The backyard features a beautiful covered patio and backs up to farmland. This outdoor space can be an ideal spot for relaxation, entertaining guests, or enjoying outdoor activities while being sheltered from the elements.
